msgstr "CTF [client] 2026"

#: templates/index.html:20
msgid "Hack the track."
msgstr "Hack the track."

#: templates/index.html:24
msgid ""
"\n"
"      As part of the Cycling World Cup, your company is responsible for "
"securing\n"
"      the industrial systems of one of the sites hosting the event.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"      Dans le cadre de la Coupe du monde de cyclisme, votre société est "
"chargée de sécuriser\n"
"      les systèmes industriels de l’un des sites accueillant l’événement.\n"
"      "

#: templates/index.html:31
msgid ""
"\n"
"      Industrial supervision, critical equipment, automation, exposed "
"networks, and real-time pressure:\n"
"      your teams must stay in control while the competition is in full "
"swing.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"      Supervision industrielle, équipements critiques, automatismes, réseaux "
"exposés et pression temps réel :\n"
"      vos équipes devront garder le contrôle pendant que la compétition bat "
"son plein.\n"
"      "

#: templates/index.html:40
msgid "Enter the arena"
msgstr "Entrer dans l’arène"

#: templates/index.html:44
msgid "View scoreboard"
msgstr "Voir le classement"

#: templates/index.html:48
msgid "Join the CTF"
msgstr "Rejoindre le CTF"

#: templates/index.html:52
msgid "Log in"
msgstr "Se connecter"

#: templates/index.html:60
msgid "New edition"
msgstr "Nouvelle édition"

#: templates/index.html:65
msgid "National Velodrome"
msgstr "Vélodrome national"

#: templates/index.html:70
msgid "Industrial systems"
msgstr "Systèmes industriels"

#: templates/index.html:81
msgid "Your mission"
msgstr "Votre mission"

#: templates/index.html:85
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Secure the critical infrastructure of a cycling competition "
"venue.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"          Sécuriser l’infrastructure critique d’un site de compétition "
"cycliste.\n"
"          "

#: templates/index.html:93
msgid ""
"\n"
"          The velodrome is running at full speed. Supervision systems are"
" reporting weak signals,\n"
"          industrial equipment is communicating, access points are "
"multiplying, and every second counts.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"          Le vélodrome tourne à plein régime. Les systèmes de supervision "
"remontent des signaux faibles,\n"
"          les équipements industriels communiquent, les points d’accès se "
"multiplient et chaque seconde compte.\n"
"          "

#: templates/index.html:100
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Analysis, exploitation, investigation, hardening: prove that "
"your team can keep a cool head\n"
"          when the pressure rises on the track.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"          Analyse, exploitation, investigation, durcissement : prouvez que "
"votre équipe sait garder la tête froide\n"
"          lorsque la pression monte sur la piste.\n"
"          "

#: templates/index.html:111
msgid "Reconnaissance"
msgstr "Reconnaissance"

#: templates/index.html:113
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Map the environment, identify exposed services, and understand "
"the attack surface.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"          Cartographiez l’environnement, identifiez les services exposés et "
"comprenez la surface d’attaque.\n"
"          "

#: templates/index.html:121
msgid "Exploitation"
msgstr "Exploitation"

#: templates/index.html:123
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Exploit application, network, or industrial weaknesses to "
"progress through the scenario.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"          Exploitez les faiblesses applicatives, réseau ou industrielles "
"pour progresser dans le scénario.\n"
"          "

#: templates/index.html:131
msgid "Resilience"
msgstr "Résilience"

#: templates/index.html:133
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Prioritize, secure, and keep critical systems under control all"
" the way to the finish line.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"          Priorisez, sécurisez et maintenez les systèmes critiques sous "
"contrôle jusqu’à la ligne d’arrivée.\n"
"          "

